  triage:description "Two sub-issues: (1) Sprint A.7 acceptance criterion requires CLI-layer entry/completion/error events for manifest-policy execution. These structured log events are absent — the manifest-policy checker runs without dispatch_event calls for entry/completion/error lifecycle. (2) The Sub-Task 4 doc review artifact required by sprint-A7.md is absent. Fix: (a) add entry/completion/error dispatch_event calls around the manifest-policy execution path in crates/sc-lint/src/dispatch.rs or the manifest backend; (b) create the Sub-Task 4 doc review artifact per sprint-A7.md spec." ;
